msgstr "Zweite Mission der imperialen Kampagne"

#: ../../../campaigns/emp02.wmf/event:10 ../../../campaigns/emp02.wmf/event:36
#: ../../../campaigns/emp02.wmf/event:68 ../../../campaigns/emp02.wmf/event:88
